Fonts
-------
  ttf-ubuntu-font-family ttf-ms-fonts ttf-vista-fonts ttf-inconsolata
  ttf-droid gsfonts (ghostscript fonts)

Themes
--------
  faenza-icon-theme faience-icon-theme gnome-shell-theme-elegance

Applications
-------------
  dwb (web) -OR- jumanji-git (web) zathura (pdf) deadbeef (music)
  movgrab (youtube downloader) gvim (text editing)
  awf-git (preview gtk themes)

Terminal / CLI
----------------
  cmus (music) tmux (terminal multiplexer) weechat (irc)
  zsh-syntax-highlighting-git rxvt-unicode (terminal)

Games
-------
  nethack tintin (mud client) zork1 zork2 zork3 hitchhikersguide
  frotz -OR- nfrotz (play datafiles from other infocom text adventures)
  EXAMPLE: nfrotz /usr/share/hitchhikersguide/hhgg.z3 ... or download
    abandonware such as Leather Goddesses of Phobos!

Server Administration
-----------------------
  htop (more legible top) iftop (top for network interfaces)

Miscellaneous
---------------
  xcalib (set icc colour profile)

